Thanks.

4
00:01:01,352 --> 00:01:03,897
What the hell!

5
00:01:12,697 --> 00:01:14,491
Who is that? Is he okay?

6
00:01:14,574 --> 00:01:15,742
He's out of it.

7
00:01:15,825 --> 00:01:18,703
He's high out of his mind.

8
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:34,135
Hey!

9
00:01:34,219 --> 00:01:36,805
Sir, you need to control yourself.

10
00:01:38,681 --> 00:01:40,475
Hand over the cocaine.

11
00:01:41,601 --> 00:01:43,561
Not unless you have the cash for it.

12
00:01:43,645 --> 00:01:45,438
Just give it to me!

13
00:01:45,522 --> 00:01:47,315
Quit it and get out!

14
00:01:47,398 --> 00:01:48,399
Hey!

15
00:01:54,072 --> 00:01:55,406
What are you doing?

16
00:02:25,812 --> 00:02:27,355
Shut the hell up!

17
00:02:36,322 --> 00:02:38,908
It hurts!

18
00:02:56,968 --> 00:02:57,844
That's freaky.

19
00:02:57,927 --> 00:02:59,470
Should we call the police?

20
00:02:59,554 --> 00:03:00,930
Or an ambulance.

21
00:03:06,394 --> 00:03:07,520
Damn amateur.

22
00:03:07,604 --> 00:03:09,439
Learn some restraint.

23
00:03:10,023 --> 00:03:11,524
WHERE IN ROPPONGI IS THIS?
THIS IS CRAZY

24
00:03:11,608 --> 00:03:14,319
CAN'T BELIEVE WE CAN SEE THIS LIVE
THE COMMENTS WON'T STOP LOL

25
00:03:14,402 --> 00:03:15,945
THIS CLUB WILL GET CLOSED DOWN

26
00:03:18,656 --> 00:03:20,617
Stimulants, narcotics, cannabis.

27
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:24,162
People who have used these drugs

28
00:03:24,245 --> 00:03:27,624
are now estimated
to total two million in Japan.

29
